                               How Are We Doing?
     __________________________________________________________________

   In order to help us evaluate The Office of Criminal Justice Planning's
   programs and employees, we would appreciate your input regarding the
   level of service that you feel you are receiving.  We would, in
   particular, welcome comments regarding the professionalism of our
   staff, the usefulness of our resources, and suggestions on how we could
   improve our services.  However, this form is only for the critique of
   programs administered through The Office of Criminal Justice Planning.
   Please fill out the form shown below in your browser.  After completing
   the form, please click on the "submit" button and your input will be
   forwarded to the OCJP's Public Inquiry Unit.
